 h(\mu_1\otimes\ldots\otimes\mu_n)(A)=\int_A h\, d(\mu_1\otimes\mu_2\ldots\otimes\mu_n). 
 h(\mu_1\otimes\ldots\otimes\mu_n)(A)=\int_A h\, d(\mu_1\otimes\mu_2\ldots\otimes\mu_n)\\=\int_{A_1}\ldots\int_{A_n}h_{\omega_1\times\ldots\times\omega_{n-1}}(\omega_n)\, d\mu_n(\omega_n)\ldots\, d\mu_1(\omega_1)\\=\int_{A_1}\ldots\int_{A_n}h_1(\omega_1)\cdot h_2(\omega_2)\cdot\ldots\cdot h_n(\omega_n)\, d\mu_n(\omega_n)\ldots\, d\mu_1(\omega_1)\\=\prod_{i=1}^{n}h_i\mu_i(A_i) 
